Notes.Text:
This update for libcap fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2023-2602: Fixed improper memory release in libcap/psx/psx.c:__wrap_pthread_create() (bsc#1211418).
- CVE-2023-2603: Fixed an integer overflow or wraparound in libcap/cap_alloc.c:_libcap_strdup() (bsc#1211419).

Vulnerabilities.Description: A vulnerability was found in the pthread_create() function in libcap. This issue may allow a malicious actor to use cause __real_pthread_create() to return an error, which can exhaust the process memory.
